abdulazeespr/Brainly-frontend-.summary: Abdulazeespr has been actively updating the Brainly frontend repository, introducing new features such as Brain page, Connect to backend, Signin and Signup, and Sidebar. Recent commits include fixes for conflicts and refactorings to improve code organization.

abdulazeespr/Brainly.summary: The Brainly repository has seen significant updates with Abdulazeespr adding features such as index page, outdir, dist config, and vercel.json. They have also resolved errors and made improvements to the repository.

abdulazeespr/care_fe.summary: Recent commits to the care_fe repository include fixes for login errors and bugs in the Public Patient Registration Form. Abdulazeespr has also updated dependencies and resolved OTP send workflow issues.

ohcnetwork/care_fe.summary: ohcnetwork submitted a pull request to the care_fe repository, proposing changes to use cn and variants for AlertDialogAction. The request includes updates to product documentation, UI text, and QA process.
